author: Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III
title: High school football preview
text: By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III The Free Press By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III Posted Oct. 8, 2015 at 9:25 PM Updated at 9:56 PM By Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III Posted Oct. 8, 2015 at 9:25 PM Updated at 9:56 PM On this edition of the Free Press Football Show Bryan Hanks and Junious Smith III preview all of this week's games, including the Greene Central/Ayden-Grifton matchup and the Kinston/South Lenoir tilt. They also talk to Jones Senior head football coach John Davis about retiring Covair Frost's jersey this Friday night.
